{"title":"python3-进制转换及zfill函数和列表倒置的特殊方法.md","slug":"python3-进制转换及zfill函数和列表倒置的特殊方法","date":"2019-08-10T13:14:37.000Z","updated":"2019-08-10T14:13:11.994Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/python3-进制转换及zfill函数和列表倒置的特殊方法.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"进制转换的问题：<br>主要用到的函数有：bin(),oct(),int(),hex()<br>","covers":null,"content":"<p>进制转换的问题：<br>主要用到的函数有：bin(),oct(),int(),hex()<br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<p>#其他进制转成十进制：</p>\n<p>#二进制转成十进制：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">int(&apos;100&apos;,2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：4</span><br><span class=\"line\">#注意输入的数值一定要是字符串的形式，第二个参数表示输入数值为二进制</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>#八进制转成十进制：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">int(&apos;04&apos;,8)</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：4</span><br><span class=\"line\">#注意输入的数值一定要是字符串的形式，第二个参数表示输入数值为八进制</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>#十六进制转成十进制：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">int(&apos;0x4&apos;,16)</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：4</span><br><span class=\"line\">#注意输入的数值一定要是字符串的形式，第二个参数表示输入数值为十六进制</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>#十进制转成二进制：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bin(int(&apos;4&apos;,10))</span><br><span class=\"line\">#或者</span><br><span class=\"line\">bin(4)</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：0b100</span><br><span class=\"line\">#0b表示二进制，如果想要截取，可以用[2:]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>#十进制转成八进制：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">oct(int(&apos;4&apos;,10))</span><br><span class=\"line\">#或者</span><br><span class=\"line\">oct(4)</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：04</span><br><span class=\"line\">#0表示八进制</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>#十进制转成十六进制：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hex(int(&apos;4&apos;,10))</span><br><span class=\"line\">#或者</span><br><span class=\"line\">hex(4)</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：0x4</span><br><span class=\"line\">#0x表示十六进制</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>#zfill函数：<br>str.zfill(width)<br>字符串扩展函数。width为扩展的宽度,扩张之后字符串右对齐，左侧填充0,和rjust(width,’0’)相似<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&quot;123&quot;.zfill(5)</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：00123        </span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;123&quot;.rjust(5,&apos;2&apos;))</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：22123  </span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;123&quot;.ljust(5,&apos;2&apos;))</span><br><span class=\"line\">#结果为：12322</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>#列表逆置特殊方法：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">list=[1,2,3,4,5]</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(list[::-1])</span><br><span class=\"line\">#输出[5,4,3,2,1],表示所有列表元素逆置</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(list[4:2:-1])</span><br><span class=\"line\">#输出[5,4],表示从下标为4到2(不包括2)的元素逆置</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}